OL,5, The true story of an artist who began  
OL,6, painting with his mouth after an       
OL,7, accident left him paralysed is to be   
OL,8, made into a stage musical.             
OL,10,FThe Little Big Things, based on Henry  
OL,11,FFraser's memoir of the same name, will 
OL,12,Fopen in London in September.           
OL,14,FFraser told BBC News he was "incredibly
OL,15,Fexcited and nervous" about the prospect
OL,16,Fof seeing his story depicted on stage. 
OL,18,FThe show will star Ed Larkin as Fraser 
OL,19,Fand play for 12 weeks from 2 September 
OL,20,Fat Soho Place.                         
